[normal]ABOUT AGEAS[bold]&#xa0;[bold]1.1
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Ageas is the second largest motor insurer in the 
[normal]UK
[normal] by number of vehicles insured. It insures over 3.5 million vehicles though its underwriting businesses Ageas Insurance Limited and Tes
[normal]co Underwriting Limited, its joint venture with Tesco Bank.
[normal]&#xa0;[bold]1.2
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Ageas also has a presence in the retail sector, through its Ageas Insurance Solutions (Cover Direct, Auto Direct and Done Deal brands), Ageas 50 (RIAS and Castle Cover brands), Kwik Fit Insurance
[normal] Services, Express Insurance and The Green Insurance 
[normal]Company broker businesses.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
